  ('optometrist-moex-00012', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-114-aa93ddf5', 'sub-optometrist-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關Bailey-Lovie視力表的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["各行比例恆定", "每行字數固定", "字母間距與字母大小同比例", "結果呈現以視角來表示，亦即視角越大，視力越好"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5093f492e448", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f33d754e2a74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "109", "s": "0905", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "低視力學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00013', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-114-aa93ddf5', 'sub-optometrist-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '什麼情況下最適合轉介病人去接受低視能諮詢？', '["只在法律性眼盲時", "當一個病人視力小於0.5或是病人有對比度下降或視野缺損時", "只有當病人要求轉介到視覺復健中心時", "當病人無法閱讀印刷品時"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5093f492e448", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f33d754e2a74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "109", "s": "0905", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "低視力學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
